      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "[unclear] APPROXIMATELY TWO FIFTY A. M. , AUGUST ONE LAST HAVING BEEN CAUSED",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "BY ANY SABOTAGE. THEY STATE THEIR INVESTIGATION INDICATES THE LEFT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "ENGINE BURNED OUT AN EXHAUST STACK WHICH CAUSED THE WING TO BURN AND",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "BREAK OFF. THE LEFT WING AS IT [unclear] BROKE OFF TORE OFF THE TAIL AND",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
