      "text": "INTELLIGENCE OFFICERS OF THE FOURTH AIR FORCE WHO WERE RETURNING FROM",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "MCCORD FIELD, WN., TO HAMILTON FIELD, CALIFORNIA. THE CREW CHIEF AND",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "A HITCHHIKER PARACHUTED TO SAFETY FROM THE PLANE. ONLY FOUR MEMBERS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "WERE ABOARD THE PLANE, DAVIDSON AND BROWN BEING PILOT AND CO- PILOT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
